text: Matylda Ossadnik (17 March 1917 - 15 May 1997) was a Polish gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:1997 deaths Category:Polish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Poland Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bytom
